sub_title: Service Performance Analyst | PGDip in Finance | Certified Public Accountant
summary:
Analytical, results-driven professional focused on finance and committed to ethical values. I consider myself as an organized and responsable person. I have seven years of working experience on finance and demonstrated skills in quantitative analysis.

Highly adept at handling various responsibilities by prioritizing my tasks, establishing clear deadlines and finding creative solutions to eliminate obstacles. I never waiver in my contribution to my team as I am always ready to help out my co-workers to achieve the end result.

I got my CPA degree at Universidad de la República and the diploma of specialization in finance at Universidad ORT. Both prestigious universities are located in Uruguay. 
 
It is my goal to continue to learn and grow throughout my professional career. While I have developed a level of expertise in broker's back and middle office, there is so much more I want to explore. I am looking for an opportunity that allows me to keep growing in the financial world.
